values:
okay so last night was matt's 22nd birthday... so we drank some at his house & then went out.... we had a pretty good time like always... i got home around 2:00 AM and passed out.... this morning i woke up to go to class... and when i got closer to my car i realized that someone had hit my car! i am so pissed i had to call the cops and get a police report made... this sucks... my car is brand new and some punk ass bitch fucked it up.... grrr.... so anyways i missed class and now i am in a cleaning mode... 

tonight a bunch of us are going to barley island to see michael & zach's band play... it should be fun....

tomorrow night i am hanging out with tom.... we are going to get his halloween costume...

friday i already had plans to go over to jake's for their big halloween party and i was just informed that bubbaweener is playing in lafayette that night... so hopefully i will be able to catch them play too! i am excited for everyone to see my costume... it's grrrrreat! i don't know if it will outdo last years though... 

saturday night i have to work & hopefully will make it over to tom's halloween party here at bsu.... just depends when i get off of work.......

** life's not a garden.... so quit bein a hoe **
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/5245.html

okay so it's been a little while since i've last updated... and i haven't really been busy.. just haven't felt like updating.... well it's friday & i just took a test... it's now officially fall break! so a weird thing happened to me yesterday while i was walking to class.... i saw something on the ground and as i got closer to it... i realized that it was a flyer with my ex boyfriend on it saying he is playing at bsu soon.... just then i look up and there's another one on the wall! they are everywhere! when i got home i got a phone call from valerie saying she just saw some flyers for him on campus.... it was really weird... but anyways so last friday night a bunch of my friends came to ball state to see bubbaweener play... so i hurried home from work so i could hang out with them.... it was a lot of fun... then saturday night i worked & went to purdue to hang out with my boys.... it was a pretty fun weekend... monday night i went out with tom for his 21st... it was a lot of fun... we sang karaoke... tonight i have to work & then i'm going to hurry back here to go out with everyone for tom's birthday.... tomorrow night i have to work & then i am going out with katrina, michaela, and katy for a girls night... i really hope i don't run into gary... katrina informed me yesterday that he is still in love with me & talks about me all the time to her... i think it would be much easier to deal with if he hated my guts.... i don't need any guys right now.... i just need to be single for a while... i really haven't been single for a long ass time.... i usually jump from guy to guy.... i'm going to stop looking for someone because usually you will find something when u least expect to. the south pole closes wednesday... so all you kids better go get some good food before they are closed & new owners take over! my last day there is saturday.... it's kinda sad.... i will try to update sometime soon... peace out kids! 


** Someday, someone will walk into your life and make you realize why it never worked out with anyone else **

so yesterday linds & i went searching for a new place to live... it is just too scary living in this neighborhood... but i think we finally found a place! hopefully we can move in soon! 

last night i went home for jill's 21st birthday... it was so much fun! we went to quite a few different bars & ended up at bdubs.... that's where she works... all the people there are really nice... we ended up getting a lot of free drinks & got really trashed... jill puked outside of some strip club... puke & rally!

oh my gosh we have to get out of this neighborhood.... some kids from across the street were just on our porch and were yelling at each other & stuff... we are in the ghetto! greg had to go outside & shut them up! 

well i just got a phone call from an old fling... i guess he is coming to muncie friday night.... hopefully i will get out of work early enough to come hang out... 

so i found out that gary stayed the night with his ex last night.... that is so funny considering he was trying to tell me they were just "friends".... what an asshole... i'm so glad i have now realized how much better i can do...

where do i begin??? well i am now 22... i don't really feel much older... i have had a pretty exciting weekend... friday night my friends and gary threw a kegger for me... at about midnight gary wanted to go to bed when about 30 people were still at the house... and he got pissed at me because i wanted to stay up and have fun at my birthday party... well i went up to his room and he is on the phone with his ex gf... what the fuck... so to make a long story short i ended up beating the shit out of him... seriously... i even have a bruised up hand to prove it.... i have never felt that much anger before... it was kinda scary... he was so mad that i beat him up that he said he was going to call the cops on me... so my friend michael came and picked me up & let me crash at his place.... i'm glad that i have awesome friends like him.... i'm really done with gary.... he has ruined my birthday 2 years in a row... that is some fucked up shit.... anyways so saturday i was supposed to go out with everyone in indy but i decided it would be better if i didn't put myself in a situation where i might see gary... so katrina & i ended up going to purdue for the night... it was so much fun.... i always end up having a blast when i go there... my guy friends really helped me to realize that i don't need someone like gary in my life...we got really trashed...i mean REALLY trashed... most of the people left or went to bed but katrina, bryce, and i made up songs while jeff & ryan played the guitar... i wish we would have recorded them.... they were hilarious! katrina ended up going to bed around 5 something while bryce, ryan, jeff, & i stayed up until 6 in the morning! i got 3 hours of sleep before i had to wakeup & drive katrina home.... bot was i hung over sunday.... and then we had to go to barley island for my family birthday party.... all of a sudden i hear some of my friends on stage singing happy birthday and natalie and christy walk out with a cheesecake and balloons and a bunch of presents for me... they are the best! i love it there... it is like we are all one big family there... i got lots of good stuff and ended up staying after my family left to drink.... my friend josh came up there and took me home later that night.... so what started out being a horrible birthday weekend.... ended up being a really memorable one! thanx everyone for being there for me this weekend! i love you guys!!
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/3624.html

well it sure has been a while.... i have been a busy girl! let's see what has happened lately.... every weekend i have been going home to work at barley island... i love it there... the people are so much fun & i make pretty good $$! usually after work i will go stay at katrina, gary, katy & rory's house... yeah that's right.... gary is now living with my best friend.... i thought i wouldn't like it at first... but things with gary are going really well and it's nice that i can hang out with him & also hang out with my best friend at the same time... and not have to take special time out for each of them.... my birthday is this weekend.... we are having a big party at their house friday night... saturday night we are going to a bar in castleton to see this cover band play that i like... and sunday we are partying at barley island! everyone's invited!! elli is huge now & we live in the ghetto... but it's a really nice house :) really big! well i don't really know what else to say.... so i'm going to go watch the presidential debate... peace out kids
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/3435.html

okay so it's been a long ass time since i have updated this motha.... so here we go... i have been working a lot lately... been hanging out with my ex bf gary... kinda weird how that happened... wednesday night i went out with josh for his 21st... it was fun... we got free drinks like all night! thursday i went to the yellowcard/something corporate/the format show... it was badass! friday night i worked and went over to chad's & drank with the gang.... saturday night we went to purdue to party at jeff & ryan's... well i'm sure you all already know how that night ended... cops busted the party & everyone that was under 21 got a ticket... somehow tom & i were outside when the cops busted the party so he is one lucky boy! but everyone else got minor consumption tickets... it sucked... sunday we had a birthday party for my mammaw... monday i had an interview at Logan's Roadhouse in noblesville.... i hope i get that job! and then i went to gary's for the night... i had to work tonight & now i'm back at home in muncie... suzie is still running great.... i'm ready for this semester to be over with! one month of summer classes & then i will be free for the summer... woo hoo! well that's all the news for right now.... i'll update soon i promise!
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/3156.html

so i'm way behind on posting on this thing.... first i'll start out with the most important news... i got a new car! she is badass... 2004 Suzuki Forenza... she's silver & i already named her.. Suzie.... i love her... she only had like 80 miles on her! brand spankin' new! hell yeah! so needless to say i have been driving everywhere.... wednesday night katrina called me & told me that her apartment got broken into & they took just about everything... so i drove to indy to stay with her... we ended up staying at katy & rory's.... & guess who happened to be there... gary (my ex).... it was nice to see him since i hadn't since the break up.... he told me that he missed me & that he was sorry.... he knows he fucked up... anyways who knows where that is going... we hung out last night too... i got to see his mom and everyone i hadn't seen since we broke up... it was nice... i had to work last night & we were busy as fuck! it sucked.. tonight i have to work & then i'm going to hang out over at andy & matt's... saturday i'm supposed to go to castleton with tom and who knows what else that night... sunday i have to work... so catch me if u can! peace out kids...
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/2922.html

well let's see... i haven't updated in a while... what did i do this weekend... well thursday night i worked at the SP... hung out at chad's... drove to muncie... took a test on friday... drove home to work... then went to chad's & drank a little... i cut off all of my hair... saturday we went rollerskating & my car died on the way... it sucked... rosemary's sick :( then my parents inform me that it is time for me to start looking for a new car... woo hooo!!! so saturday jill & i looked around kokomo at some car dealerships... then that night we all partied at andy's... it was a lot of fun... until i got sick... yuck... sunday we had easter dinner at my mammaw's & i found $22 worth of eggs! woo hooo! then mom & i went lookin around at more car dealerships... we found some good deals... that night i went over to chad's & hung out... tom & i went & checked out some more car places in elwood... and then i came home... & now i'm waiting on my mom to get off of work & we are going to lafayette to look at the honda dealership there... wish me luck!
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/2709.html

okay so i know it's Tuesday & i haven't updated for a while.... i have had a busy weekend... so friday i took a quiz.. hurried home to go to work... after work i went to chado's and drank quite a bit... it was pretty fun.... i hung out with someone i hadn't seen in years! saturday i had a bad bad hangover... so i slept most of the day away... ashlee came home & we went to trav's little get together... after that we went back over to chado's to hang out.... sunday i worked... then went to chado's.... monday i decided to stay home & babysit for my nieces... then i had to work... then i watched the game at chado's... my sister won the little pool we had goin... woo hoo! i woke up at 8:00 this morning & drove back to muncie... went to class... came home & took a nap.... i am worn out! right now i am watching american idol... i have to write a paper tonight... I have a huge presentation thursday.. a test friday... this semester sucks.... my classes are hard.... i want it to be overwith... oh yeah so that i can start summer classes... blah... anyways i'm going to go watch american idol... peace out kids
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/2402.html

okay so i'm about to head to bed... but i'm sure i won't have time to post over the weekend... so i will do it now... well tonight i hung out with trav, both jessicas, brittni, gabe, and jeff.... it was pretty fun... we pulled some April Fools jokes on people... then the dude that i used to date called me & we talked for like an hour on the phone... tomorrow i have to work... then i'll probably go hang out at chado's... saturday we have my cousin's baby shower to go to... my sister is coming home & we are going to trav's that night... then i have to work sunday.... well that's going to be my eventful weekend! peace out kids..... hope everyone has a good weekend

ps.. i have a quiz in the morning.... wish me luck!
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/2283.html

alright so i forgot to tell u guys that yesterday the ex called me at 8:00 in the morning! i could have killed him! he thought he was so funny.... anyways... jill came over & we hung out for a while... i ended things with justin... finally..... i went out to a karaoke bar  with kacy & rusty... it was a lot of fun... some of rusty's friends ended up meeting up with us... some dude bought our drinks all night! can't beat that! we ended up singing like 5 songs.... last kiss by pearl jam... you outta know by alanis morrisett... i like it i love it by tim mcgraw... i clogged for everyone while kacy & rusty sang Sold... and we ended the night with sweet home alabama... classic... it was a pretty fun night... except some weird dude was hitting on me so i told him that chris was my bf so he would leave me alone... why do i attract all the weirdos? so anyways i'm totally single now... that means this weekend is going to be full of fun! :)
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/2042.html

today has been a shitty day.... finished up a paper for class.... did my accounting homework & turned that in.... i hate that class.... tutored Carol... my little 3rd grader... she wasn't in a very good mood today... the instructer made me take out my nose ring... i have been tutoring there for like 5 weeks now & she is just now telling me i can't wear it.... it's raining outside... my mom called me with bad news.... it's just been a shitty day... but luckily enough kacy came to the rescue & just informed me that if i go out with her & rusty tonight some dude is buying all our drinks..... so i'm looking forward to that! anyways i'm going to work on some homework so i can go out tonight... fun fun! Elli just pooped outside... she's such a smart little girl! :) 

yay of the day: josh brought me some badass cd's to burn... he's the shit!
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/1619.html

i worked on a project today... took a test.... & i just got home from chado's..... we watched american idol & hung out for a while.... so i get back and i have this message from the chic that jer cheated on me with..... wow i think that girl is stalking me.... how did she get my screen name? anyways she is all pissed off i guess because i wrote about her in here... i guess i'm not supposed to be mad that some scandelous girl fucked around with a dude while i was dating him.... and i guess it doesn't make you a slut for doing that either.... wow i don't know what u would call it then.... any suggestions?
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/1371.html

okay so here goes my eventful night... worked on homework.... studied for a test... played with the puppy.... so justin calls... and i thought we were totally overwith.... i mean our conversation the other night seemed as if that's what was going on.... and i ask him "so is this the end or what?" and he acts like i'm an idiot for even thinking that... i'm so gosh darn confused.... it isn't going anywhere... but for some reason neither of us will just end things.... i need to get out & start looking for someone new.... i had an awesome conversation with a dude from west lafayette tonight... hopefully we will get to talk again soon.... 


"standing on the edge of morning 
scent of sex and new found glory 
playing as she's pulling back her hair 
she drives away 
she's feeling worthless 
used again but nothing's different

home by three

http://angballstate.livejournal.com/1152.html

well it's monday & i'm back at school.... let me just update you on my weekend... friday night i worked.... then went out to some bars with jeremiah, danny, braun, and kevin... it was pretty fun... i got pretty drunk & ended up passing out at some dude's house waitin on kevin to come get us... i woke up saturday morning with one hell of a hangover... then i caught an ex bf driving by my house in tipton... it was pretty funny.... so i talked to him for a little while & we exchanged new phone numbers.... it was really weird because i hadn't seen him a few years.... but it was nice to talk to him... so that night i went with jill to chado's.... we hung out and i saw ONE of the girls who jer cheated on me with.... not very impressed by her... it was really hard for me not to beat the shit out of her... but she's like 16 so i would have went to jail for that one... haha... i am amazed by all the slutty girls that end up over at chad & cody's.... it really grosses me out.... it makes me not want to go over there anymore... hopefully since their break is over they won't be around as much.... all we can do is hope.....

so sunday i worked & it was such a beautiful day out.... so we were busy as hell... right now i'm playin with Elli... she's gettin big! i have a ton of homework to do tonight & study for a test.... fun fun fun

oh yeah & i think i'm done with the boy.... he really pissed me off this weekend... surprise surprise...
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/858.html

hey guys... boy has my day been exciting.... typed out a paper... went to class... went to work.... stopped by chado's now i'm back home in muncie.... i should be studying... i'm so sick of school... i hate studying... i hate going to class... oh well only a few more years of it.... i have an accounting test tomorrow... that class is so hard... our puppy is asleep... she's so cute... anyways i'm working in t-town tomorrow & then i will be going out with my good buddy jeremiah for a few drinks.... don't get to go to nashbash with my ruggers... but i need to be makin $$ rather than spendin it... i'm a poor college kid.... anyways i think i am done with the boy... he is just too damn confusing & there's always gotta be drama with him... should have known... well gotta go study... peace out kids...
http://angballstate.livejournal.com/688.html

hey ya'll it's ang.... decided that this livejournal thingy looked like some fun.... anyways nothing's really new.... my roomate got a puppy & she is the cutest thing ever! her name is Elli.... i have some pictures of her at http://groups.msn.com/halloweenweekend/pictures check it out! well better work on some homework... peace out kids...
